href="#icon-8a75e9205b2d7697ad826d592ebf05f0"></use></svg><span class="label">Get My Landing Page Now</span></a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div id="container03" class="container-component instance-3 style-3 default"><div class="wrapper"><div class="inner" data-onvisible-trigger="1"><p id="text10" class="text-component instance-10 style-3">Prop Find</p><h2 id="text03" class="text-component instance-3 style-2">Most Property Agents Look the Same Online</h2><p id="text02" class="text-component instance-2 style-1"><span style="color: #0071E3">Today, most agents only use property portals.</span> But portals promote properties — not you.</p><div id="list01" class="list-component instance-1 style-1"><ol><li><p><span style="color: #0071E3"><strong>You Are Hard to Find and Easy to Forget</strong></span> - When clients search your name on Google, they mostly see old portal listings, incomplete profiles, and many competing agents beside you. Your experience and achievements are buried in crowded pages, so clients do not see your true value.</p></li><li><p><span style="color: #0071E3"><strong>You Look the Same as Every Other Agent</strong></span> - On property portals, agents appear interchangeable. Buyers message many agents at once and compare mainly on price. Even if you are skilled and professional, you only have seconds to make a first impression online — and most agents lose that moment.</p></li><li><p><span style="color: #0071E3"><strong>You Do Not Control Your Online Presence</strong></span> - Your professional image lives on platforms you do not own. If a portal changes its layout, pricing, or rules, your visibility can drop overnight. You are renting space instead of building a long-term professional identity.</p></li></ol></div><ul id="buttons07" class="buttons-component instance-7 style-1"><li><a href="#purchase" class="n01" role="button"><svg aria-labelledby="buttons07-icon-1-title"><title id="buttons07-icon-1-title">Arrow Down (Light)</title><use xlink:href="#icon-8a75e9205b2d7697ad826d592ebf05f0"></use></svg><span class="label">Get My Landing Page Now</span></a></li></ul></div></div></div><div id="container08" class="container-component instance-8 style-1 default"><div class="wrapper"><div class="inner" data-onvisible-trigger="1"><p id="text01" class="text-component instance-1 style-3">Prop Find</p><h2 id="text40" class="text-component instance-40 style-2">A Simple Way to Look Professional Online</h2><p id="text41" class="text-component instance-41 style-1">We build clean, professional landing pages made for property agents. <span style="color: #0071E3">Each page is designed to help clients understand who you are and what you offer — in seconds.</span></p><hr id="divider06" class="divider-component instance-6 style-1"><h3 id="text42" class="text-component instance-42 style-7">Your Digital Name Card</h3><h2 id="text44" class="text-component instance-44 style-2">Agent Personal Page</h2><p id="text08" class="text-component instance-8 style-10"><span style="color: #0071E3">One professional link that introduces you to clients.</span></p><div id="list03" class="list-component instance-3 style-1"><ol><li><p>Your photo and introduction</p></li><li><p>Awards and credentials</p></li><li><p>Testimonials from clients</p></li><li><p>Featured listings or sold properties</p></li><li><p>Clear WhatsApp contact button</p></li></ol></div><p id="text35" class="text-component instance-35 style-6">This is the link you share everywhere — WhatsApp, Instagram, flyers, and email.</p><ul id="buttons12" class="buttons-component instance-12 style-1"><li><a href="https://jasontandemo.propfind.me/" target="_blank" class="n01" role="button"><svg aria-labelledby="buttons12-icon-1-title"><title id="buttons12-icon-1-title">Link</title><use xlink:href="#icon-49c7b76f0edfabe10e324ba1ac396f84"></use></svg><span class="label">Demo</span></a></li></ul><hr id="divider07" class="divider-component instance-7 style-1"><h3 id="text46" class="text-component instance-46 style-7">A Focused Page for the Right Buyer</h3><h2 id="text07" class="text-component instance-7 style-2">Property Campaign Page</h2><p id="text51" class="text-component instance-51 style-10"><span style="color: #0071E3">A dedicated landing page designed to attract a specific target audience for each property.</span></p><div id="list04" class="list-component instance-4 style-1"><ol><li><p>Large property photos that highlight lifestyle benefits</p></li><li><p>Key selling points written for the target buyer</p></li><li><p>Location advantages that matter to that audience</p></li><li><p>Clean layout with no competing distractions</p></li><li><p>Simple enquiry form or WhatsApp button for fast response</p></li></ol></div><p id="text49" class="text-component instance-49 style-6">Instead of showing the same message to everyone, the page speaks directly to the ideal buyer — whether it is families, investors, or first-time homeowners.</p><ul id="buttons06" class="buttons-component instance-6 style-1" style="flex-wrap:nowrap;"><li><a href="https://jasontandemo.propfind.me/retire/" target="_blank" class="n01" role="button"><svg aria-labelledby="buttons06-icon-1-title"><title id="buttons06-icon-1-title">Link</title><use xlink:href="#icon-49c7b76f0edfabe10e324ba1ac396f84"></use></svg><span class="label">Demo: Retire</span></a></li><li><a href="https://jasontandemo.propfind.me/family/" target="_blank" class="n01" role="button"><svg aria-labelledby="buttons06-icon-2-title"><title id="buttons06-icon-2-title">Link</title><use xlink:href="#icon-49c7b76f0edfabe10e324ba1ac396f84"></use></svg><span class="label">Demo: Family</span></a></li></ul></div></div></div><p id="text06" class="text-component instance-6 style-3">Prop Find</p><h2 id="text48" class="text-component instance-48 style-2">HOW IT WORKS?</h2><p id="text29" class="text-component instance-29 style-10"><span style="color: #0071E3">Simple 3 Steps</span></p><div id="list02" class="list-component instance-2 style-1"><ol><li><p>Send us your details</p></li><li><p>We design your landing page</p></li><li><p>You start sharing your link</p></li></ol></div><ul id="buttons03" class="buttons-component instance-3 style-1"><li><a href="#purchase" class="n01" role="button"><svg aria-labelledby="buttons03-icon-1-title"><title id="buttons03-icon-1-title">Arrow Down (Light)</title><use xlink:href="#icon-8a75e9205b2d7697ad826d592ebf05f0"></use></svg><span class="label">Get My Landing Page Now</span></a></li></ul><div id="container01" data-scroll-id="purchase" data-scroll-behavior="previous" data-scroll-offset="0" data-scroll-speed="3" data-scroll-invisible="1" class="container-component instance-1 style-1 default"><div class="wrapper"><div class="inner" data-onvisible-trigger="1"><p id="text11" class="text-component instance-11 style-3">Prop Find</p><h2 id="text12" class="text-component instance-12 style-2">💸 Simple, Transparent Pricing — No Hidden Fees</h2><p id="text13" class="text-component instance-13 style-1"><span style="color: #0071E3">Affordable and Clear Pricing — it’s that easy..</span></p><hr id="divider02" class="divider-component instance-2 style-1"><h3 id="text27" class="text-component instance-27 style-3">Agent Personal Page</h3><h2 id="text20" class="text-component instance-20 style-2">$10 per year</h2><ul id="buttons02" class="buttons-component instance-2 style-3"><li><a href="https://wa.me/6587423466" class="n01" role="button"><svg aria-labelledby="buttons02-icon-1-title"><title id="buttons02-icon-1-title">WhatsApp</title><use xlink:href="#icon-e9633646f45121eab610a3d30c929019"></use></svg><span class="label">WhatsApp</span></a></li></ul><hr id="divider04" class="divider-component instance-4 style-1"><h3 id="text19" class="text-component instance-19 style-3">Property Campaign Page</h3><h2 id="text25" class="text-component instance-25 style-2">$20 per year</h2><ul id="buttons13" class="buttons-component instance-13 style-3"><li><a href="https://wa.me/6587423466" class="n01" role="button"><svg aria-labelledby="buttons13-icon-1-title"><title id="buttons13-icon-1-title">WhatsApp</title><use xlink:href="#icon-e9633646f45121eab610a3d30c929019"></use></svg><span class="label">WhatsApp</span></a></li></ul></div></div></div><div id="container04" class="container-component instance-4 style-4 default full screen"><div class="wrapper"><div class="inner" data-onvisible-trigger="1"><p id="text14" class="text-component instance-14 style-3">Prop Find</p><h2 id="text17" class="text-component instance-17 style-2">Still in doubt?</h2><p id="text18" class="text-component instance-18 style-6">Please Whatsapp Us Directly!</p><ul id="buttons01" class="buttons-component instance-1 style-3"><li><a href="https://wa.me/6587423466" class="n01" role="button"><svg aria-labelledby="buttons01-icon-1-title"><title id="buttons01-icon-1-title">WhatsApp</title><use xlink:href="#icon-e9633646f45121eab610a3d30c929019"></use></svg><span class="label">WhatsApp</span></a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div>
